==製作==
電影計畫首次於2013年7月15日被提出<ref>July 15, 2013 DeVita, Joe, "Slipknot’s Shawn ‘Clown’ Crahan to Make Feature Film Directing Debut With ‘Officer Downe’" (http://loudwire.com/slipknots-shawn-clown-crahan-feature-film-directing-debut/ {{Wayback|url=http://loudwire.com/slipknots-shawn-clown-crahan-feature-film-directing-debut/ |date=20190419093950 }}) Loudwire. Accessed 15 May 2016.</ref>。2015年2月20日，{{le|金·寇茲|Kim Coates}}被證實將擔任主演<ref>Fleming Jr, Mike, February 20, 2015, "http://deadline.com/2015/02/kim-coates-officer-downe-sons-of-anarchy-1201378290/ {{Wayback|url=http://deadline.com/2015/02/kim-coates-officer-downe-sons-of-anarchy-1201378290/ |date=20220408164631 }}" (http://deadline.com/2015/02/kim-coates-officer-downe-sons-of-anarchy-1201378290/ {{Wayback|url=http://deadline.com/2015/02/kim-coates-officer-downe-sons-of-anarchy-1201378290/ |date=20220408164631 }}) [[Deadline.com|Deadline]]. Accessed 15 May 2016.</ref>。其餘的演員於2015年4月1日宣布，包括[[山姆·維特威|山姆·維特威]]、{{le|琳賽·帕西法|Lindsay Pulsipher}}與{{le|雷諾·威爾森|Reno Wilson}}<ref>April 1, 2015, Bowar, Chad, "More Cast Members Announced for Shawn ‘Clown’ Crahan Directed Film ‘Officer Downe’" (http://loudwire.com/more-cast-members-shawn-clown-crahan-film-officer-downe/ {{Wayback|url=http://loudwire.com/more-cast-members-shawn-clown-crahan-film-officer-downe/ |date=20210506100616 }}) Loud Wire. Accessed 15 May 2016.</ref>。而電影則由[[滑結樂團|滑結樂團]]的{{le|沙恩·克拉汗|Shawn Crahan}}執導。

拍攝於2015年3月開始。而原作漫畫作者之一的{{le|喬·凱西|Joe Casey}}將為電影撰寫劇本<ref>Ferrell, Cody, March 13, 2015	"JOE CASEY GIVES AN UPDATE ON THE OFFICER DOWNE MOVIE" ({{cite web |url=http://www.screengonzo.com/2015/03/13/joe-casey-gives-an-update-on-the-officer-downe-movie/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-10-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521102201/http://www.screengonzo.com/2015/03/13/joe-casey-gives-an-update-on-the-officer-downe-movie/ |archivedate=2015-05-21 }}) Screen Goonz. Accessed 15 May 2016.</ref>。電影劇照於2015年5月13日和15日釋出<ref>May 15, 2015, Emily, "FIRST LOOK AT OFFICER DOWNE – DIRECTED BY SLIPKNOT’S CLOWN" (http://www.kerrang.com/31465/first-look-officer-downe-directed-slipknots-clown/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.kerrang.com/31465/first-look-officer-downe-directed-slipknots-clown/ |date=20160707002118 }}) [[Kerrang|Kerrang]]. Accessed 15 May 2016.</ref>。監製[[馬克·奈維代|馬克·奈維代]]證實，這部電影將被評為R級<ref name="#1"/>。

